Subject: Re: [T2] 79 Type 2 turn signal problems.

Hi Andrew,

Check the flasher can. You need a 3-prong flasher in a 1979 bus. A leak 
from the windshield or the fresh air intake grille can fill the flasher 
can with water, which will cause the symptoms you describe. A small 
hole drilled in the bottom of the flasher can will prevent water from 
accumulating in it.

Happy trails,

Greg Potts
